From 48f29870ef42339cef3310d7f1d047d416227c4f Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Willy Tu <wltu@google.com>
Date: Tue, 24 Mar 2026 15:14:33 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] reduce image size by moving to Multi-call Binary
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

This is done to reduce the daemon size when installed on a SPI flash.
The goal is to
- Reduced ELF Overhead
- Shared Libraries/Static Linking
- Shared Common Code

Tested:
```
